    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine and the desirable 6-speed manual transaxle. This wide-body 996.2 variant utilizes a rear-biased viscous coupling AWD system for superior lateral acceleration. The IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump. The chassis remains composed on Bilstein B6 dampers, providing excellent feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Minor stone chipping is present, but the drivetrain is mechanically sound with no bore scoring or RMS leaks. A true driver-spec example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
