      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more adventures with a new owner. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, comfy car without the brand-new price tag. Come say hi and take it for a test drive!",
